Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.45,0:00:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.42,0:00:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Is someone there?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.67,0:00:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyone? Help me, please! Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.43,0:00:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,My dear sister, I guess\Nthat means you're conscious again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.85,0:00:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}How are you doing in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.77,0:00:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you dreaming of something pleasant?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.32,0:00:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,MY HAPPY MARRIAGE
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.99,0:02:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,EPISODE 6\NDETERMINATION AND THUNDER
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.75,0:02:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you drive any faster?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.41,0:02:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Getting upset right now\Nwon't change anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.63,0:02:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,so settle down.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.09,0:02:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You're acting awfully calm about this.\NThey might've hurt her, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.76,0:02:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}She's your fiancée,\Nshouldn't you at least be upset?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.97,0:02:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Before we arrive,\Nyou're positive she's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.85,0:02:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Yes. Miyo is at the Saimori's.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.64,0:02:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You were really trying\Nto get in your beauty rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.40,0:02:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}It was taking you\Nsuch a long time to wake up
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.48,0:02:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}that I was wondering\Nif your heart had just stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.03,0:02:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh... Why are you doing this?\NWhat is it I did?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.61,0:03:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Annoying as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.33,0:03:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I had thought you'd be spending\Nyour days working as a servant,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.62,0:03:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,or dying like an animal\Non the side of the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.62,0:03:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You must think you're better than us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.46,0:03:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, girl.\NYou will step down as Mr. Kudo's fiancée.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.46,0:03:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.92,0:03:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You will repeat these exact words to him,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.09,0:03:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,"I reject, and wish to leave\Nthis arranged marriage with you."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.51,0:03:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I was thinking, the responsibility\Nof being Mr. Kudo's wife
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.43,0:03:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,is too much for you to bear,\Nmy dear sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.90,0:03:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That blue kimono you're wearing\Nis as beautiful as the summer sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.74,0:03:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think\Nit's ill-suited for you though?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.28,0:03:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on. Promise me\Nthat you'll reject these arrangements.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.25,0:03:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Or else I'll have to alter\Nthis precious, precious kimono.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.25,0:03:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Since it looks so awful on you,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.84,0:03:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,you would force me\Nto make it match the person wearing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.39,0:04:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have the gall to ask him
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.01,0:04:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,to buy you\Nsuch an expensive kimono for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.60,0:04:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,then rejecting the marriage arrangements\Nwould be a piece of cake, wouldn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.27,0:04:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,When I get engaged to Mr. Kudo,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.56,0:04:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,then you can finally have Koji\Nall to yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.78,0:04:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Now then, Sister, tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.36,0:04:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}the next time you see Mr. Kudo,\Nwhat will you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.66,0:04:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.95,0:04:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,No?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.33,0:04:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.55,0:04:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.34,0:04:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,- That wasn't what I said.\N- No!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.67,0:04:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- No!\N- You already know what to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.80,0:04:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna hear you say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.85,0:04:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to hear those words\Nexactly from your mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.23,0:04:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"I do not want this marriage arrangement."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.19,0:04:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.69,0:05:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why is this happening?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.78,0:05:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It would be easy to give up\Nand do what they told me.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.16,0:05:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But it's the only thing in so long{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.50,0:05:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}that I've wanted...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.46,0:05:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...for myself.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.00,0:05:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Something wrong?\NDid you lose your voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.92,0:05:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You're just as useless\Nas you've always been, Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.89,0:05:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.64,0:05:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.73,0:05:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I won't...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.23,0:05:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What you're asking me, I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.57,0:05:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}How dare you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.07,0:05:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You brat...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.74,0:05:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.12,0:05:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll handle this, don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.42,0:06:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,See, I knew you would look better\Nas a crumped mess down on the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.68,0:06:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen. Did you forget\Nwhat a failure you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.85,0:06:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Not only do you not have Spirit-Sight,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.97,0:06:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,but you never had\Nany good traits to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.39,0:06:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an absurd idea\Nwhen you think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.06,0:06:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The embarrassment of our family\Nis the one that gets to marry Mr. Kudo?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.28,0:06:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hey! Open up!\N-{\i1}Wouldn't you agree{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.28,0:06:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}this is the better deal?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.24,0:06:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not only do you get to stay\Nat the Saimori house,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.24,0:06:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,but you also get to have Koji\Nall to yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.25,0:06:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,just like you've always wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.75,0:06:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I... I want...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.04,0:06:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I want...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.17,0:06:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.13,0:06:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,...my Lord Kudo...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.51,0:06:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Kiyoka Kudo's fiancée.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.64,0:06:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}He's not yours, now or ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.89,0:06:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You gotta be kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.39,0:06:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had enough of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.73,0:06:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the one who raised you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.48,0:07:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,All these years of your ingratitude!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.40,0:07:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}And as soon as you get a husband,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.36,0:07:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}you start spewing this nonsense?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.90,0:07:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You're as wretched as I thought you were!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.16,0:07:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You will not ruin this!\NMy life will not be ruined
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.37,0:07:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,because a horrible little girl\Ndoesn't know her place.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.04,0:07:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In the past,\NI would've already... apologized to them,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.67,0:07:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}praying for the storm to pass...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.42,0:07:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That was the life I lived.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.01,0:07:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was easier, so I was quiet.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.93,0:07:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But that's not my life anymore.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.43,0:07:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.31,0:07:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}changed.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.31,0:07:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Changed into someone stronger than I was.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.52,0:07:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I chose him.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.19,0:07:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And he chose me!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.07,0:07:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.86,0:07:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,- Huh?\N- You should stand back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.95,0:07:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What a stubborn little welp you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.45,0:07:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.29,0:08:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.33,0:08:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What... have you done?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.59,0:08:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.63,0:08:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.30,0:08:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.64,0:08:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Kudo? Wait! Wait a moment! Stop, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.72,0:08:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.22,0:08:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Mr. Saimori, where's Miyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.85,0:08:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.27,0:08:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyo is done with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.98,0:08:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kudo family will not see her again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.23,0:08:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,How could you? Father, how could you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.61,0:08:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiyoka Kudo. I didn't expect you\Nto get here so quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.41,0:08:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you keeping my fiancée?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.37,0:08:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyo has no interest in marrying you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.33,0:08:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,She said that she will not return.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.37,0:08:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I intend to face her myself\Nand ask if that's what she wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.00,0:08:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You should tell me where she is or move.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.01,0:08:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.80,0:08:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're not going to listen\Nto what I say,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.26,0:08:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,then you and I are facing an impasse.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.22,0:08:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have to use force\Nif you won't step aside.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.64,0:08:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang on! Please just wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.89,0:09:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Tatsuishi, what is going on?\NWhat's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.52,0:09:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Once this is over,\Nyou can ask your daughter about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.11,0:09:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The main entrance has been destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.90,0:09:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,If you allow him to proceed any further,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.24,0:09:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,he'll destroy the entirety of your home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.41,0:09:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,If you wish to keep a roof over your head,\Nlend me a hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.30,0:09:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.80,0:09:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,As I expected from the head of the Kudos.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.57,0:09:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,This is pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.66,0:10:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true what they say. You're a monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.37,0:10:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You're in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.54,0:10:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Now move.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.89,0:10:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Father's no match for him.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.93,0:10:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's like an adult facing an angry child.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.56,0:10:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That power...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.98,0:10:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's known as the strongest gift-user\Nof our time for a reason!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.95,0:10:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that? That light?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.96,0:10:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You... You disgust me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.17,0:10:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and say it already!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.88,0:10:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,"I will reject the marriage arrangements\Nwith the Kudo family."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.05,0:10:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I won't lie because you say to...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.80,0:11:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You worthless brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.39,0:11:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you. You know exactly\Nwhat your place is in this world!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.15,0:11:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.40,0:11:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I refuse to say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.11,0:11:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,My fiancé wants me there!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.94,0:11:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,He knows that I belong...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.91,0:11:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.91,0:11:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Storehouse?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.99,0:11:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.58,0:11:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,There's an old storehouse in the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.16,0:11:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,They barely use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.46,0:11:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's unassuming,\Nso Miyo could be in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.00,0:11:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Show me the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.38,0:11:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.81,0:11:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Stand down now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.65,0:11:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,My father!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.19,0:11:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't a safe place to be using fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.90,0:11:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,How many more foolish decisions\Nwill he make?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.08,0:12:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Is... this worth it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.71,0:12:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I will not let you marry an Usuba!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.05,0:12:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's how it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.94,0:12:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,He was rendered unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.24,0:12:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Now let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.62,0:12:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It didn't need to be this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.21,0:12:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and say it already!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.46,0:12:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Say you'll reject him this instant!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.13,0:13:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Say it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.84,0:13:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In the past, I would wait,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.43,0:13:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}hoping the next moment\Nwould lead to my last breath.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.60,0:13:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Every day was such a struggle.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.31,0:13:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Being alive hurt...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.48,0:13:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}to the point that my heart went numb.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.53,0:13:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Living was exhausting.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.78,0:13:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Back then, I believed...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.28,0:13:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}there was no place where I belonged.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.95,0:13:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm glad...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.08,0:13:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was wrong.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.04,0:13:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I want you to stay with me\Nuntil death separates us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.38,0:13:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I belong somewhere.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.30,0:13:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I will be by his side.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.68,0:13:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and spit it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.43,0:13:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I will...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.93,0:13:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}never say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.85,0:13:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.11,0:13:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I've decided that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.61,0:14:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I will be with him until my final breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.46,0:14:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that... Mr. Kudo?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.72,0:14:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.93,0:14:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He really... came for me.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.48,0:14:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Do you see?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.52,0:14:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lord Kudo,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.77,0:14:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I didn't give up this time.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.07,0:14:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.70,0:14:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Kudo, are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.50,0:14:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you're safe now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.42,0:15:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You really came all this way for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.42,0:15:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It was worth it to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.72,0:15:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you all so very... much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.32,0:15:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What on earth? What is it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.79,0:15:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But I... No, the house...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.29,0:15:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.38,0:15:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,How did she get like this?\NWhat did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.13,0:15:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,She didn't bow to you\Nand you decided to beat her for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.22,0:15:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you want from her?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.14,0:15:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I'm not the one... None of this is my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.06,0:15:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to...\Nto correct a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.69,0:16:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing else happened, that was it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.15,0:16:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Mistake?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.19,0:16:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister doesn't possess Spirit-Sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.11,0:16:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,She's boney and ragged
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.82,0:16:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and is useless as a servant.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.24,0:16:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That has to be why she could never be\Na good match for the Kudo family,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.12,0:16:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,so it must be a big mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.08,0:16:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I know I'm the better choice for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.04,0:16:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother and Father wouldn't just say\NI'm the greatest!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.13,0:16:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}They've told me\Nthat I'm the opposite of my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.75,0:16:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That I'm superior to her\Nin every possible way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.38,0:16:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Shut your mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.84,0:16:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.97,0:16:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to hear\Nany more of your putrid drivel.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.27,0:16:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But... why don't you understand\Nwhy you should be with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.61,0:16:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.36,0:16:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I not just say
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.90,0:16:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard enough of your horrid nonsense?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.74,0:16:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I would not and will never marry\Nan arrogant woman like yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.91,0:16:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if the very heavens demanded it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.37,0:17:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Now go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.14,0:17:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Why choose her?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.89,0:17:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}How could things have ended like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.52,0:17:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaya, we need to evacuate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.73,0:17:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm right. I know I'm right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.57,0:17:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go of me! Just go and leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.65,0:17:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Just shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.24,0:17:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What? How dare you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.95,0:17:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Sister was the only one\Nyou ever liked anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.70,0:17:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You should just go evacuate with her,\Nso you can forget about me already!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.54,0:17:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right.\NIt's just like you said.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.67,0:17:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The only person\NI care about in this world is Miyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.38,0:17:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But the truth is...\Nthat if you die here today,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.97,0:17:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyo will grieve for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.26,0:17:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,because that's who she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.85,0:18:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.10,0:18:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,No, we all did this to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.73,0:18:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I just... I can't let you hurt her again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.25,0:18:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You're taller than the last time, Miyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.59,0:18:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mother! It's you!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.84,0:18:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I am so sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.59,0:18:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,for making you endure\Neverything all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.01,0:18:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.89,0:18:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Believe in yourself\Nfor the rest of your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.52,0:18:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Believe in that power
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.23,0:18:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}- that lives within you.\N- Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.11,0:18:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Believe in...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.32,0:18:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}what power?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.21,0:19:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What terrible news!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.38,0:19:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,How detestable!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.25,0:19:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,As utterly awful as imaginable!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.55,0:19:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Tatsuishi was completely useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.22,0:19:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate, Kudo will get ahold\Nof the Usuba bloodline.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.81,0:19:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Majesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.56,0:19:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It is time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.44,0:19:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We must ask your permission for a request.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.36,0:19:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I beg you. Allow us to achieve\Nwhat we've been hoping for all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.82,0:19:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,To put things back where they belong.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.53,0:19:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,A ripple effect will begin soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.37,0:19:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I grant the permission you seek.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.46,0:19:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,However, do not miss this opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.54,0:19:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Your Majesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.63,0:19:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Then we shall proceed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.34,0:19:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We will begin the operation as planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.30,0:20:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You must destroy
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.85,0:20:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,the accumulation of power no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.90,0:20:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.70,0:20:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.17,0:20:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, Lord Kudo...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.92,0:20:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.46,0:20:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Kudo, it's you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.30,0:20:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.51,0:20:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't push yourself. Lie down.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.22,0:20:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.72,0:20:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.07,0:20:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you're all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.78,0:21:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I am, but, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.57,0:21:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Lord Kudo, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.91,0:21:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}This was all...\NI was careless with the amulet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.66,0:21:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}No need to blame yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.16,0:21:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}None of this... is your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.46,0:21:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,None of this was ever your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.43,0:21:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much, Lord Kudo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.64,0:21:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,My Lord Kudo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.93,0:21:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Miss Miyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.77,0:21:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Yurie.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.61,0:21:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Miyo! I'm so glad!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.78,0:21:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,- You've finally woken up.\N- But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.70,0:21:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Yurie, you don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.95,0:21:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You really don't need to cry, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.91,0:21:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You've no idea\Nhow worried I was about... you, Miss Miyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.67,0:21:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're okay now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.42,0:22:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I agree.\NI'm glad you're home safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.51,0:22:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
